              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Yes. vinFMEA fully supports the AIAG-VDA harmonized FMEA methodology, including the 7-step approach, Action Priority (AP) ratings, and all required documentation fields for IATF 16949 compliance.</p>
            </div>
