            <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-5 text-left">
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">What's the difference between SFMEA, DFMEA, and PFMEA?</span>
              <svg class="faq-chevron h-5 w-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer px-5 pb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">SFMEA (System) analyzes system-level interactions, DFMEA (Design) focuses on component design risks, and PFMEA (Process) addresses manufacturing process failures. vinFMEA supports all three with full traceability between them.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-d3 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white">
