            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer px-5 pb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Floating licenses are shared across your team. If you have 5 licenses, any 5 team members can use vinFMEA simultaneously. When someone logs out, the license becomes available for another user. This maximizes value for larger teams.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-d4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white">
